=== 场发射源及其真空电子器件 ===
早在2002年，垂直于基底表面的石墨烯纳米墙就被成功制备出来。<ref name="Adv.Mater.">{{cite journal|year=2002|doi=10.1002/1521-4095（20020104）14:1<64::AID-ADMA64>3.0.CO;2-G|journal=Adv.Mater.|volume=14|page=64-67|title=Carbon nanowalls grown by microwave plasma enhanced chemical vapor deposition|author=Wu, Y.H. ''et al.''}}</ref>它被看作是非常优良场致发射电子源材料。<ref name="JMC">{{cite journal|year=2004|journal=Journal of Materials Chemistry|volume=14|page=469-477 |title=Carbon nanowalls and related materials|author=Wu, Y.H. ''et al.''|url=http://www.rsc.org/delivery/_ArticleLinking/DisplayArticleForFree.cfm?doi=b311682d&JournalCode=JM|format=free download pdf}}</ref>  最近关于单片石墨烯的电场致电子发射效应也见诸报道。<ref name="APL">{{cite journal|year=2010|doi=10.1063/1.3291110|journal=Appl. Phys. Lett.|volume=96|page=023106|title=Fabrication of graphene nanogap with crystallographically matching edges and its electron emission properties|author=Wang, H.M. ''et al.''|url=http://www3.ntu.edu.sg/home/YuTing/papers/APL-Graphene%20FE.pdf|format=free download pdf|access-date=2010-03-30|archive-date=2012-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527205119/http://www3.ntu.edu.sg/home/yuting/papers/APL-Graphene%20FE.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

